Allergan Inc, a subsidiary ofSmithkline Beckman Corp, said the U.S. District Court in NewYork has ordered Bausch and Lomb Inc to immediately recall fromretail shelves all soft contact lens solutions sold under the"HYPO-CARE" name and cease any further distribution.    The company said the court found that HYPO-CARE was tooclose to Allergan's trademark "HYDROCARE" to prevent publicconfusion. Reuter&#3;